### Argp++ (version 0.9.0)

   This is the initial public release.

   A C++ wrapper class library around the GNU C-language **argp** options 
   parsing library for command-line programs.

   Project URL on Github:
   https://github.com/bobhairgrove/Argp-plus-plus
   
   Please read the files README, INSTALL, and the HTML docs in the 
   `doc` subfolder for further details about installation and use of the 
   library. The file `ChangeLog` will contain more details about the latest
   developments.
   
   Written by Robert Hairgrove. Copyright (c) 2017 by Robert Hairgrove and
   the Free Software Foundation. All feature requests and bug reports are
   welcome and should be sent to Robert Hairgrove <code@roberthairgrove.com>
   or create an issue at Github under the project URL mentioned above.

